room_title: Escape room "Flashback " by Time to Escape in Denver
room_description:
The year is 1989 and someone or something has kidnapped the visionary behind time travel technology
She left behind an invaluable relic that powers a complex time machine.
Can you solve her puzzling security protocols and retrieve the relic before it falls into the wrong hands?
We caution you….this time portal is a one way ticket. You’ll be on your own to find your way back to the present!
